Sentence: Shadab Rayeen is an Indian sound engineer.
His best known work is the mix of Ae Dil Hai Mushkil.
He has been honoured with the "Best Recording Engineer Award" in the category of Technical Awards for the mix of Ae Dil Hai Mushkil by International Indian Film Academy Awards.
